description: Ever wonder what it would be like to hire male stripper Zack Lemec for a private show? Well, we decided to offer you the opportunity to experience it, as close as possible to the real thing. From the moment Zack arrives to your room till he showers after his performance, you won't miss a thing! Sit down, drop your pants and feel the excitement, Zack's here for you!
title: Stripper Service 5 (feat. Zack Lemec), Scene #01
